column2: Duos Technologies Group, Inc. is focused on designing, developing and providing proprietary intelligent technologies. The Company operates under the brand names, duostech and truevue360. Duostech is engaged in developing, marketing and deploying technologies and systems that capture, process and present users with a number and types of data that provide its customers with a range of technology solutions. With a focus on security, inspection and operations for infrastructure, it targets a range of industries, including transportation, retail, law enforcement, oil, gas and utilities. truevue360 is its artificial intelligence (AI) program. Through duostech brand, it provides a range of technologies, including Intelligent Railcar Inspection Portal (rip), Vehicle Undercarriage Examiner (vue), Thermal Undercarriage Examiner (t-vue), Pantograph Inspection System (apis) and Intelligent Analytics Suite (praesidium).
